snippet.title: The Manhole Masterpiece Edition for iOS Trailer
snippet.description:
Introducing The Manhole for iOS (iPhone™, iPod touch®, and iPad.) From the creators of Myst, The Manhole is a silly, delightful, interactive, busy-box-of-a-world that kids can explore and explore - finding something new around every corner.

This award-winning romp transports children to the fanciful world around, above, and beneath what appears to be just an average, everyday, manhole. But there is much more than meets the eye - have tea with a rabbit, wake up a walrus, nibble biscuits with a dragon, hang with a penguin, boat with an elephant, speak French with a turtle, and much more!

 Visit The Manhole website here:  http://www.cyanworlds.com/iOS_ManholeME/The_Manhole_iOS/Welcome.html
